'''雷克斯·韦恩·蒂勒森'''<ref name=ckxxw/>（{{lang-en|Rex Wayne Tillerson}}，{{bd|1952年|3月23日}}），生於美国[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]]北部的[[威奇托福爾斯_(德克薩斯州)|威契塔瀑布城]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dallasnews.com/business/business/2014/09/06/exxon-mobil-ceo-rex-tillerson-an-eagle-scout-to-the-core|title=Exxon Mobil CEO Rex Tillerson an Eagle Scout to the core - Business - Dallas News|date=September 6, 2014|publisher=|access-date=2016-12-11|archive-date=2019-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190722210920/http://www.dallasnews.com/business/business/2014/09/06/exxon-mobil-ceo-rex-tillerson-an-eagle-scout-to-the-core|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://familysearch.org/ark:/61903/1:1:V6S5-GLP |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-12-11 |archive-date=2017-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170126121402/https://familysearch.org/ark:/61903/1:1:V6S5-GLP |dead-url=no }}</ref>，美國著名企業家。[[土木工程師|土木工程師]]出身，1975年加入[[埃克森美孚|埃克森美孚後]] (Exxon Mobil) ，並一路攀升成為[[埃克森美孚|埃克森美孚]]集團2006年到2016年的[[董事長|董事長]]兼[[執行長|執行長]]<ref>[http://www.exxonmobil.com/Corporate/about_who_mgmt_rwt.aspx Rex W. Tillerson] {{Wayback|url=http://www.exxonmobil.com/Corporate/about_who_mgmt_rwt.aspx |date=20131012195354 }}. ExxonMobil. Retrieved on June 28, 2012.</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Chart: The Largest Companies by Market Cap Over 15 Years|url=http://www.visualcapitalist.com/chart-largest-companies-market-cap-15-years/|date=August 12, 2016|accessdate=December 9, 2016|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228073705/https://www.visualcapitalist.com/chart-largest-companies-market-cap-15-years/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曾於2017年2月1日至2018年3月31日間，受美國總統特朗普指派出任[[美國國務卿列表|第69任]][[美國國務卿|美國國務卿]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180313/s00005/1520946876240|title=特朗普解僱國務卿蒂勒森　提名中情局長接任|date=2018-03-13|publisher=[[明報|明報]]|accessdate=2018-03-13|archive-date=2018-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615083225/https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180313/s00005/1520946876240|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/973540316656623616 |title = Mike Pompeo, Director of the CIA, will become our new Secretary of State. |work = Donald J. Trump |publisher = [[Twitter|Twitter]] Inc. |date = 2018-03-13 |language = en |accessdate = 2018-03-13 |archive-date = 2018-06-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180618170209/https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/973540316656623616 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==生平==
===早年生活===
提勒森於1952年3月23日於[[威奇托福爾斯_(德克薩斯州)|威契塔瀑布城]]出生，父親為巴比·喬·提勒森（Bobby Joe Tillerson），母親為派蒂·蘇·巴頓（Patty Sue Patton）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://familysearch.org/ark:/61903/1:1:V6S5-GLP|title=Texas Birth Index, 1903–1997|work=FamilySearch Database|date=December 5, 2014|accessdate=December 15, 2016|archive-date=2017-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170126121402/https://familysearch.org/ark:/61903/1:1:V6S5-GLP|dead-url=no}}</ref>。提勒森的父母以當時擅演牛仔角色的好萊塢影星{{link-en|雷克斯·艾倫|Rex Allen}}與[[約翰·韋恩|約翰·韋恩]]為他命名<ref>Filkins, Dexter (October 16, 2017). [https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2017/10/16/rex-tillerson-at-the-breaking-point "Rex Tillerson at the Breaking Point"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2017/10/16/rex-tillerson-at-the-breaking-point |date=20210321153748 }}. ''The New Yorker''</ref>。提勒森小時候在{{link-en|維農市|Vernon, Texas}}、[[斯蒂爾沃特_(俄克拉何馬州)|靜水市]]等地長大，後來又因父親在[[美國童軍|美國童軍]]工作的關係搬家到[[亨茨維爾_(德克薩斯州)|亨茨維爾]]。<ref name="codys">{{cite news|author=Cody Stark|title=Huntsville High School graduate Rex Tillerson: 'An All-American kid'|url=http://www.itemonline.com/news/local_news/huntsville-high-school-graduate-rex-tillerson-an-all-american-kid/article_24eb750c-973b-59d8-a70c-e5c23d9c7fc3.html|accessdate=April 2, 2017|work=The Huntsville|date=December 23, 2016|archive-date=2021-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330190410/https://www.itemonline.com/news/local_news/huntsville-high-school-graduate-rex-tillerson-an-all-american-kid/article_24eb750c-973b-59d8-a70c-e5c23d9c7fc3.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="nahal">{{cite news|author=Nahal Toosi|title=Who is Rex Tillerson?|url=http://www.politico.com/story/2017/01/who-is-rex-tillerson-233362|accessdate=April 1, 2017|work=[[Politico|Politico]]|date=January 11, 2017|archive-date=2019-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191229152156/https://www.politico.com/story/2017/01/who-is-rex-tillerson-233362|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="theal">{{cite book|title=The Alcalde|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0-MDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA47|accessdate=April 2, 2017|date=November 2007|publisher=Emmis Communications|page=47|archive-date=2020-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200830221700/https://books.google.com/books?id=0-MDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA47|dead-url=no}}</ref>他有兩名姊妹<ref name="pbpost">{{cite news|author1=Debbie Lord|title=Read Rex Tillerson's opening statement during the Senate confirmation hearing|url=http://www.palmbeachpost.com/news/national/read-rex-tillerson-opening-statement-during-the-senate-confirmation-hearing/brvmU4tnpdHSjTHEmxvAWP/|accessdate=April 1, 2017|work=Palm Beach Post|date=January 11, 2017|archive-date=2017-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812125021/http://www.palmbeachpost.com/news/national/read-rex-tillerson-opening-statement-during-the-senate-confirmation-hearing/brvmU4tnpdHSjTHEmxvAWP/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，分別為雷·安·漢米爾頓（Rae Ann Hamilton）是住在德州[[阿比林_(德克薩斯州)|阿比林]]的內科醫生<ref name=abi>{{cite news|title=Tillerson's sister says he would do 'an incredible job'|url=http://www.reporternews.com/story/news/local/texas/2016/12/13/tillersons-sister-says-he-would-do-incredible-job/95396250/|accessdate=April 1, 2017|work=Abilene Reporter News|date=December 13, 2016|archive-date=2021-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330190333/https://www.reporternews.com/story/news/local/texas/2016/12/13/tillersons-sister-says-he-would-do-incredible-job/95396250/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及喬·琳·彼得斯（Jo Lynn Peters）則是在高中從事教職。<ref name="pbpost"/>

===初入職場===
1975年畢業於[[得克萨斯大学奥斯汀分校|得克萨斯大学奥斯汀分校]]的[[土木工程|土木工程]]學，取得[[學士|學士]]學位<ref name="utexas">{{cite web |url=http://www.engr.utexas.edu/alumni/distinguished-alumni/deg/2006 |title=2006 Distinguished Engineering Graduate: Rex W. Tillerson, B.S.C.E. 1975, Chairman and CEO, Exxon Mobil Corporation |publisher=Cockrell School of Engineering, University of Texas |access-date=2016-12-11 |archive-date=2018-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180331021248/http://www.engr.utexas.edu/alumni/distinguished-alumni/deg/2006 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

踏入職場後，首先成為美孚公司的工程師<ref name=exxon>{{cite web |url=http://corporate.exxonmobil.com/en/company/about-us/management/rex-w-tillerson |title=ExxonMobil: Rex Tillerson |publisher=[[Exxon_Mobil|Exxon Mobil]] |access-date=2016-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161226100400/http://corporate.exxonmobil.com/en/company/about-us/management/rex-w-tillerson |archive-date=2016-12-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

====能力展現====
1989年，提勒森已成為埃克森石油公司美國中部生產部的總經理。1995年，提勒森任埃克森葉門分公司、[[埃索|埃索探勘]]暨[[呵叻|呵叻]]生產公司（Esso Exploration and Production Khorat Inc.）董事長。

到了2006年，提勒森被選為[[埃克森美孚|埃克森美孚]]集團[[董事長|董事長]]兼[[CEO|CEO]]，接掌這間當時盈餘全世界第六高的大公司<ref name=ckxxw>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cankaoxiaoxi.com/ym/20161214/1518186.shtml |title=12月14日译名发布：Rex Tillerson |author= |date=2016-12-14 |publisher=参考消息网 |language= |accessdate= |quote= |archive-date=2017-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171127233353/http://www.cankaoxiaoxi.com/ym/20161214/1518186.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年至2012年間，曾任{{link-en|美國童軍團主席|List of national presidents of the Boy Scouts of America}}，該職是美國童軍團非執行職的最高階。

2014年，時任埃克森美孚集團董事長兼CEO的提勒森曾代表公司和[[俄羅斯總統|俄羅斯總統]][[佛拉迪米爾·佛拉迪米羅維奇·普丁|普丁]]洽談生意，提勒森當時就表態反對{{link-en|制裁俄羅斯|International sanctions during the Ukrainian crisis}}。提勒森也曾經是美俄合資的{{link-en|埃克森石油天然氣公司|Exxon Neftegas}}其中一名董事。

====退休====
2017年1月1日，從埃克森美孚集團退休。

