|全球暖化]]表示懷疑<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/CHRG-111hhrg76003/pdf/CHRG-111hhrg76003.pdf |title= THE EXXONMOBIL-XTO MERGER: IMPACT ON U.S. ENERGY MARKETS |access-date= 2016-12-11 |archive-date= 2018-10-12 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181012141113/https://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/CHRG-111hhrg76003/pdf/CHRG-111hhrg76003.pdf |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Schwartz |first=John |date=August 19, 2016 |title=Exxon Mobil Fraud Inquiry Said to Focus More on Future Than Past |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/20/science/exxon-mobil-fraud-inquiry-said-to-focus-more-on-future-than-past.html |newspaper=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |access-date=August 23, 2016 |archive-date=2021-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511142652/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/20/science/exxon-mobil-fraud-inquiry-said-to-focus-more-on-future-than-past.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年12月13日，美國總統當選人[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]宣布將提名蒂勒森擔任[[美國國務卿|美国国务卿]]，此前蒂勒森从未担任过公职，也从未从事过外交工作<ref name=ckxxw/>。

由于蒂勒森和特朗普就一系列外交问题看法分歧严重<ref>[http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43388981 特朗普突然换国务卿 欧盟担心美欧贸易战] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43388981 |date=20190416002036 }}.BBC中文网.[2018-03-14].</ref>，2018年3月13日，美国总统特朗普通过推特宣布，將解除蒂勒森美国国务卿职务，并委派时任中情局局长[[邁克·蓬佩奧|邁克·蓬佩奧]]接任该职<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/973540316656623616|title=Mike Pompeo, Director of the CIA, will become our new Secretary of State. He will do a fantastic job! Thank you to Rex Tillerson for his service! Gina Haspel will become the new Director of the CIA, and the first woman so chosen. Congratulations to all!|accessdate=2018-03-14|date=5:44 AM - 13 Mar 2018|last=Trump|first=Donald J.|work=@realDonaldTrump|language=en|archive-date=2018-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618170209/https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/973540316656623616|dead-url=no}}</ref>。蒂勒森成為美國有史以來第一位被總統解職的美国国务卿。

