提勒森結過兩次婚。第一任妻子與他育有一對雙胞胎兒子，但後來離婚。<ref name="codys"/><ref name=sco>{{cite book|author=Steve Coll|title=Private Empire: ExxonMobil and American Power|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=AipuCoT96yQC&pg=PT137|accessdate=April 2, 2017|date=May 1, 2012|publisher=Penguin Publishing Group|isbn=978-1-101-57214-6|page=137|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926110604/https://books.google.com/books?id=AipuCoT96yQC&pg=PT137|dead-url=no}}</ref>1986年提勒森與倫達·聖克萊爾結婚，倫達也因上一段婚姻育有一子。<ref name=sco/> 1988年，倫達與提勒森誕下一子。<ref name=sco/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.referenceforbusiness.com/biography/S-Z/Tillerson-Rex-W-1952.html#b|title=Rex W. Tillerson biography|last=Cordon|first=Matthew C.|work=Encyclopedia of Business, 2nd ed.|accessdate=January 23, 2012|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304112520/http://www.referenceforbusiness.com/biography/S-Z/Tillerson-Rex-W-1952.html#b|dead-url=no}}</ref>提勒森的雙胞胎兒子長大後都成為工程師，都有德州大學奧斯汀分校[[科克雷爾工程學院|科克雷爾工程學院]]的理學士學位。<ref name="codys"/><ref name=cocse>{{cite web|title=Tillerson Family Commits $5 Million to Cockrell School of Engineering, Bolsters Engineering Education and Research Center|url=https://news.utexas.edu/2014/04/15/tillerson-family-commits-5-million-to-cockrell-school|work=University of Texas|accessdate=April 2, 2017|date=April 15, 2014|archive-date=2017-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170403014902/https://news.utexas.edu/2014/04/15/tillerson-family-commits-5-million-to-cockrell-school|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2006年，提勒森獲德州大學頒發傑出工程畢業生的頭銜。<ref name="utexas"/>

提勒森住在{{link-en|巴頓維|Bartonville, Texas}}。<ref name="cand">{{cite news|author=Candy Evans|title=Rex Tillerson Bought the Late Charles Wyly's Equestrian Ranch in Argyle: Horse Country Just Got Hotter|url=http://candysdirt.com/2016/12/16/will-rex-tillersons-new-job-make-bartonville-even-hotter-horse-country/|accessdate=March 29, 2017|work=CandysDirt.com|date=December 16, 2016|archive-date=2021-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215152303/https://candysdirt.com/2016/12/16/will-rex-tillersons-new-job-make-bartonville-even-hotter-horse-country/|dead-url=no}}</ref>被指派為國務卿後，提勒森在華盛頓特區的[[卡洛拉马_(华盛顿哥伦比亚特区)|卡洛拉馬]]買房置產。<ref>{{cite news|author=Benjamin Freed|title=Rex Tillerson Buys $5.6 Million Kalorama Home|url=https://www.washingtonian.com/2017/02/22/rex-tillerson-buys-5-6-million-kalorama-home/|accessdate=April 21, 2017|work=Washingtonian|date=February 22, 2017|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125142352/https://www.washingtonian.com/2017/02/22/rex-tillerson-buys-5-6-million-kalorama-home/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

宗教信仰方面，提勒森是[[公理會|公理會]]教徒，{{link-en|美國國家基督教公理會聯合會|National Association of Congregational Christian Churches}}的成員，該會屬於[[主流新教|主流新教]][[喀爾文主義|改革派]]的一個教派派別。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://religionnews.com/2016/12/14/rex-tillerson-establishment-protestant-secretary-of-state/|title=Rex Tillerson, Establishment Protestant secretary of state|first=Mark|last=Silk|publisher=Religious News Service|date=December 14, 2016|accessdate=February 2, 2017|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207012710/https://religionnews.com/2016/12/14/rex-tillerson-establishment-protestant-secretary-of-state/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=AipuCoT96yQC|title=Private Empire: ExxonMobil and American Power|first=Steve|last=Coll|date=2012|publisher=Penguin|via=Google Books|page=569|access-date=2018-02-02|archive-date=2019-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610044144/https://books.google.com/books?id=AipuCoT96yQC|dead-url=no}}</ref>提勒森夫妻檔曾於2012年捐出金額約5,000至10,000美金給美國國家基督教公理會聯合會下轄辦理的報紙"公理會雜誌"（The Congregationalist Magazine）。<ref>{{cite journal |volume=165 |number=3 |url=http://congregationalist.org/maguploads/magazineissue_43_tc_sept_2013_webcomp.pdf |journal=The Congregationalist |date=September 2013 |page=7 |title=Honor Roll of Distinguished Individual Donors |author= |access-date=2018-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309195812/http://www.congregationalist.org/MagUploads/MagazineIssue_43_TC_sept_2013_webcomp.pdf |archive-date=2016-03-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=CongregationalistDonor>{{cite web|url=http://congregationalist.org/Donations.aspx|title=Donations|work=The Congregationalist|accessdate=February 3, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107023953/http://congregationalist.org/Donations.aspx|archive-date=2017-11-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2014年2月20日，媒體報導提勒森夫婦加入反對在巴頓維興建水塔的陣營，當地許多居民都害怕若有了新建的水塔會鼓勵巴頓維小鎮賣水給來探勘石油或天然氣的公司，使重型工程車頻繁出入而衍生交通事故、噪音吵雜等問題。不過報導指出，上述理由都不是提勒森反對當地興建水塔的原因，他反對只是因為他覺得水塔太高很礙眼。與提勒森持相同意見，反對興建水塔的還有重量級眾議院議員{{link-en|迪克·阿邁|Dick Armey}}夫婦。<ref name="fracking_reuters">{{cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2014/02/26/us-usa-fracking-tillerson-idUSBREA1P24O20140226|title=Exxon Mobil CEO welcomes fracking, but not water tower in his backyard|first=Marice|last=Richter|work=Reuters|date=February 26, 2014|accessdate=2018-02-02|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924194020/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/02/26/us-usa-fracking-tillerson-idUSBREA1P24O20140226|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="fracking_wsj">{{cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052702304899704579391181466603804|title=Exxon CEO Joins Suit Citing Fracking Concerns|work=The Wall Street Journal|first=Daniel|last=Gilbert|date=February 20, 2014|accessdate=2018-02-02|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323021126/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052702304899704579391181466603804|dead-url=no}}</ref>興建水塔議題的正方與反方後來訴諸法律解決，不過在2014年11月，法官駁回了提勒森等人的訴求，使他們退出訴訟。<ref>{{cite news|title=Rex Tillerson drops out of water tower lawsuit in Bartonville|first=Nicholas|last=Sakelaris|work=Dallas Business Journal|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/dallas/news/2014/04/21/rex-tillerson-dropsout-of-water-tower-lawsuit-in.html|date=April 21, 2014|accessdate=November 28, 2014|archive-date=2019-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191009201653/https://www.bizjournals.com/dallas/news/2014/04/21/rex-tillerson-dropsout-of-water-tower-lawsuit-in.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

